## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c215c-186">A maioria das propriedades de <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> que tem "Capacidade" no final do nome, como <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.CollationCapability%2A>, são coleções de valores de um tipo enumerado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-186">Most of the properties of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> that have "Capability" at the end of the name, such as <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.CollationCapability%2A>, are collections of values of an enumerated type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c215c-187">Mas <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A> e <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A> são coleções de objetos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-187">But <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A> are collections of objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c215c-188">Para as duas últimas propriedades, você não pode testar a presença de um determinado valor usando o **Contains** método <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-188">For the latter two properties, you cannot test for the presence of a particular value by using the **Contains** method of <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c215c-189">Isso ocorre porque, com tipos de referência, o método retorna `true` somente quando o endereço de memória do objeto passado para ele é o mesmo que o endereço de um objeto na coleção; ou seja, eles são o mesmo objeto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-189">This is because, with reference types, the method returns `true` only when the memory address of the object passed to it is the same as the address of an object in the collection; that is, they are the same object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c215c-190">Já que isso não geralmente será o caso, o método quase sempre retornará `false` mesmo se houver um objeto na coleção com exatamente os mesmos valores em todas as suas propriedades, como o objeto passado para o **Contains** método  <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-190">Since this will not usually be the case, the method will nearly always return `false` even if there is an object in the collection with exactly the same values in all its properties as the object passed to the **Contains** method of  <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c215c-191">Para determinar o conteúdo do <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>, você deve enumerar por meio de cada um dos seus membros, compará-los com o valor desejado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-191">To determine the contents of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>, you must enumerate through each of its members, comparing them with the desired value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c215c-192">Se a impressora não dá suporte a seleção de tamanho de mídia, a coleção está vazia.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-192">If the printer does not support media size selection, the collection is empty.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c215c-193">Essa propriedade corresponde à [esquema de impressão](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)do `PageMediaSize` palavra-chave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-193">This property corresponds to the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)'s `PageMediaSize` keyword.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c215c-194">O exemplo de código a seguir mostra como pesquisar um determinado valor no <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c215c-194">The following code example shows how to search for a particular value in the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
foreach (PageMediaSize mediaSize in pc.PageMediaSizeCapability)  
    {  
        if (mediaSize.PageMediaSizeName == PageMediaSizeName.ISOA4)  
        {  
            Console.WriteLine("A4 size is supported");  
            break;  
        }  
    }  
```

  
  
